\fs18 \cf4 \cb31 \strokec4 As a child, Lucia's grandmother took her by the hand and led her into the Hollows.\cb1 \
\cb31 From that moment on, she roamed its darkened trails and hunted in its boundless depths. With her brush, she painted the Ethereals she encountered, and the glow of Ether became the brilliance that lit her childhood.\cb1 \
\cb31 "When I was little, I had three friends: the mighty black shield, the teleporting Thana, and the super-powerful great armor!"\cb1 \
\cb31 "Then one day, they were gone..."\cb1 \
\cb31 "But it's okay! I drew them in my notebook. Now, with just a wave of my staff, I can summon them all back!"\cb1 \
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

