\fs18 \cf4 \cb31 \strokec4 Lately, a tale has been spreading through New Eridu about the Night Emissary.\cb1 \
\cb31 "Every night at midnight, the Night Emissary shows up on the streets to tell us all kinds of stories!"\cb1 \
\cb31 "She's also an amazing magician! Just by chanting a spell, there's a 'Woosh!' and she summons a whole swarm of Ethereals to fight for us!"\cb1 \
\cb31 "Last time we got lost in a Hollow, the Night Emissary used that very trick to save us!"\cb1 \
\cb31 \'97As told by Avocaboo, Devilboo and Boollseye.\cb1 \
