\fs18 \cf4 \cb31 \strokec4 A Scholar of Urban Legends must have keen curiosity, plenty of drive, and the guts to set off without hesitation. Lucia is no exception.\cb1 \
\cb31 That's why, during her early days in New Eridu, she became a regular at Public Security.\cb1 \
\cb31 "How many times do I have to tell you? Chasing after ghost stories doesn't give you the right to wander into construction zones!"\cb1 \
\cb31 "Don't sleep on the streets, don't run around in the middle of the night, and don't go diving into Hollows in front of everyone... These are all part of the 'Rules for Life in New Eridu,' and you need to take them seriously!"\cb1 \
\cb31 "If you really can't sleep, then... uh, why not go explore Thymefield manor, and tell Alice a few ghost stories while you're there?"\cb1 \
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

