\fs18 \cf4 \cb31 \strokec4 Lucia's life is an endless journey. She runs beneath the moonlight, searching, crossing street after street, city after city.\cb1 \
\cb31 Stories intertwine like threads, spinning endless dreams, while gentle song flows beneath the glow of the night lanterns.\cb1 \
\cb31 Her search never stops, and under the stars, the journey goes on without end.\cb1 \
\
\cb31 Only when the night fades and the sun rises does the girl step out of the Hollows, stretching lazily.\cb1 \
\cb31 "Yaaawn... I'm so tired... but everyone says it's best not to sleep inside a Hollow..."\cb1 \
\cb31 "Maybe I should just crash on the floor at the video store instead!"\cb1 \
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

